com.hazelcast.client.spi.impl

Class ClientInvocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.client.spi.impl.ClientInvocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class ClientInvocation
extends Object
implements Runnable
    ClientInvocation handles routing of a request from client

    1) Where should request be send 2) Should it be retried 3) How many times it is retried
